  "description": "North antechamber (spawn) connected by a short corridor to a south main chamber. DOOR_EXIT north wall back to parent, DOOR south wall descends to child. Torches flank both rooms. Useful for interior floors that need a staging beat before the action (guild, inn, dispatcher's office).",
